        div.event
          h1 Object Calisthenics Validator
          p
            |Object Calisthenics was introduced 
            a(href="http://www.xpteam.com/") Jeff Bay
            |  in  
            a(href="https://pragprog.com/book/twa/thoughtworks-anthology") The Thoughtworks Anthology
            |  published by The Pragmatic Programmers.
            |The calisthenics consist of nine rules that are applied in a short coding challenge. The training focuses on Object Oriented principals. During the training the developer has to verify for himself if the his code adheres to the rules. 
            |As part of a 
            a(href="https://github.com/fabianschwarzfritz/Object-Calisthenics-Analyzer-Documentation/blob/master/documents/report/_endversion/ValidatingTheObjectCalisthenics.pdf") student research paper
            |, I analysed the rules and implemented a tool to validate the rules. The eclipse plugin adds hints and warnings to each line where the rules are broken.
                
